memorial resolution lionel remond lenox we the academic council desire to express our deep sense of loss in the death of our c page 1 memorial resolution lionel remond lenox we the academic council desire to express our deep sense of loss in the death of our colleague professor lionel remond lenox we remember with grateful appreciation his unbroken record of thirty five years of able and faithful service to the university we honor him as one of that loyal and devoted first faculty group who carried the university through its critical formative years and we shall hold in affectionate memory his kindly and unselfish spirit be it resolved that a copy of this statement of appreciation be inscribed on the minutes of the academic council and transmitted to the family of professor lenox and to the chairman of the board of trustees of the university at murray wh sloan re swain
